# v1.0 Phase 7A: a raw snapshot of the developer's real ~/.claude/settings.json
# (carries live secrets + personal paths). NOT consumed by the installer — it
# patches the user's live settings.json programmatically. A scrubbed example
# ships as claude-config/settings.example.json instead. NEVER commit the real one.
claude-config/settings.json

